This paper is primarily focused on mobile network monitoring, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses privacy and security concerns related to mobile networks, which could be classified under the sub-category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The use of mobile apps and VPN services is also discussed, which could be classified under the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the potential applications of the proposed system, such as application classification and user profiling, which could be classified under the sub-category of social and information networks (cs.SI) or performance analysis (cs.PF).
